Yemen Ruling Party Condemns Opposition’s March Plan, Saba Says

-- B y   V i v i a n   S a l a m a
-- 
2011-03-24T06:07:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-24/yemen-ruling-party-condemns-opposition-s-march-plan-saba-says.html
A march on Yemen’s presidential
palace planned for tomorrow by the Joint Meeting Parties, an
opposition coalition, shows the group’s “thirst for blood and
chaos,” according to Tareq al-Shami, who heads the information
department at the ruling General People’s Congress, state-run
Saba news agency  reported today .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vivian Salama in Abu Dhabi at 
 vsalama@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at  barden@bloomberg.net . 